                        <div class="post-title">
                                <h2><a href="" rel="bookmark" title="">About EasyGSP</a></h2>
                        </div>
                </div>
                <div class="entry">
                        <p>EasyGSP is a runtime environment for processing Groovy scripts.  &nbsp;&nbsp;It provides an easy to use, no server restart required, environment for developing web sites using groovy.
                        &nbsp;&nbsp;A website developed using EasyGSP consists of only groovy scripts: no jar, .java, .or class files. &nbsp;
                              

                        </p>
